Hello, SCP Foundation! I'm Keyii  and got steadily more and more depressing as I wrote it. I own the image so no need to worry about lawsuits there, guys. The Foundation also almost had a male Snappelganger, but the friend who I asked to be my model shot me down cold. Thus we have the article as it exists today.

I owe a huge thank you to:

Cyantreuse, for being so kind about discussing my idea in the Ideas forum!
minmin, for giving me permission to use SCP-2232 and for his extensive proof-reading,
NewyRose, for their thoughtful comments while proofreading!
thefoundationnoob, for their great suggestions in the drafts forum!


I'm very inexperienced as an SCP writer, but I would be extraordinarily pleased if anyone got any enjoyment out of this at all.

EDIT: This SCP (formerly 3439, now 3009) has changed number!! Thank you so much to talented and very kind Shaggydredlocks for offering me the slot when he decided to delete one of his stories.





